      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……\n今日も連絡はありませんわね……",
      "startTime": 3.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2763.3333333000005,
          "startTime": 6.73
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すず？　ため息なんかついてどうかしたのか？",
      "startTime": 7.6713831823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "べべ、別に、悩み事なんて何もありませんわよ！",
      "startTime": 11.7063491107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "悩み事があるのか……",
      "startTime": 16.256099852,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4977.233481300001,
          "startTime": 21.2333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10113.900148000002,
          "startTime": 26.37
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "違うと言ってるでしょう！　悩みなんてありま……\nえっ、着信？　ひょっとして……",
      "startTime": 22.4999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……日頃のご愛顧に感謝してポイント還元\nセールを開催……もう、なんですの、まぎらわしい！",
      "startTime": 32.4228821434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、誰かの連絡を待っているのか？",
      "startTime": 39.1977790118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "べ、別に待ってなんかいませんわ\n誰かの連絡で一喜一憂するほど私は暇人ではありません",
      "startTime": 45.697119236,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8202.880764,
          "startTime": 53.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それでは、レッスンがあるので\nこれで失礼いたします！",
      "startTime": 53.576322364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すずがあんなに焦るなんて……もしかして\n大事な相手からの連絡を待っているのか？",
      "startTime": 60.0523382686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さらに数日後",
      "startTime": 64.2455118895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……\nこんなに待っても連絡がないなんて……",
      "startTime": 68.466668129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（あの寂しげな表情……やはりそうだ）\n（すずが連絡を待っている相手は……）",
      "startTime": 76.6333347957,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2866.665204300006,
          "startTime": 79.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "すず……ひょっとして、好きな人が出来たのか？\nもしそうなら厳しいことを言うようだが――",
      "startTime": 85.352200035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "違います！　変な誤解をしないでくださいまし！",
      "startTime": 88.3489287137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え、違うのか？\nそれじゃあ、すずが連絡を待っている相手は誰なんだ？",
      "startTime": 95.1333297093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "それは……放課後ティータイムのみなさんですわ……",
      "startTime": 99.2148016054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達と遊ぶ約束をしたのか？",
      "startTime": 104.3594500302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "はっきりと約束した訳ではありませんが……\n打ち上げの時に、また遊びたいと言ってくれたのですわ",
      "startTime": 111.2666630427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "すず……\n世間ではそれを社交辞令と言ってだな……",
      "startTime": 116.718901474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "社交辞令ではありません！　あの様子は本気でした！\n本心から私と遊びたいと言ってくれたのですわ！",
      "startTime": 124.2473683367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに、何日経っても連絡がなくて……",
      "startTime": 128.6025982935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに遊びたいなら\nすずの方から誘ってみたらどうだ？",
      "startTime": 134.6666604995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、アイドルの私が一般の女子高生を\n遊びに誘うなんて……",
      "startTime": 141.4735852163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達も学業や部活で忙しいのかもしれませんし……",
      "startTime": 143.9203988154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すずがやきもきしているように、案外向こうも\n連絡を待っているかもしれないぞ",
      "startTime": 152.1999938328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "……確かにスーパーアイドルの私が雲の上の存在過ぎて\n遠慮していることは十分あり得ますわね",
      "startTime": 160.2333271662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ{user}さんがそこまで言うなら\n今回だけは特別に私の方から連絡して差し上げます",
      "startTime": 167.6666604995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（あっさり意見を翻したな……）\n（すずも本音では連絡したかったってことか）",
      "startTime": 175.5333271662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、なんと言って誘えばいいのでしょう",
      "startTime": 179.1804892937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "「お暇なら遊んで差し上げてもよろしいですわよ」\n……上から目線過ぎますわね",
      "startTime": 188.5666604995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "「私に連絡をしないなんて何様のつもり？」\n……たちの悪い絡みですわね",
      "startTime": 196.1999938328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_02-suz020.m4a",
